"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-31-ireland-rugby-star-shows-superhuman-strength-save-team-mate-certain-injury-paris-olympics-21331795\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"If you needed any further proof of the superhuman abilities of the Olympians competing at this summer's Games inParis, look no further\\u2026  The women's rugby sevens competition has been a compelling and brutal watch throughout, with scintillating plays, free-flowing moves and huge hits on display across the rounds in the French capital.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 335, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And while Ireland's campaign came to an end with a disappointing seventh-place play-off defeat at the hands of Team GB, there was one incredible moment from the performance which left viewers' jaws on the floor.\", \"from\": 337, \"to\": 548, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 347, \"end\": 354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9992482388969745, \"rank\": 0.000673678505819062, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 448, \"end\": 455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999859030915559, \"rank\": 1.4096224733314974e-05, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Holding an imperious 28-5 lead with just five minutes remaining on the clock, Team GB kicked off and sent the ball looping into Ireland's half in the direction of Emily Lane, who appeared to slightly misjudge its trajectory.\", \"from\": 550, \"to\": 774, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 628, \"end\": 635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999859030915559, \"rank\": 1.4096224733314974e-05, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 678, \"end\": 685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9992482388969745, \"rank\": 0.000673678505819062, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 713, \"end\": 723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emily_Lane\", \"score\": 0.9999940667929451, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emily Lane\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emily_Lane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emily_Lane\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris 2024 Olympics  Thankfully, Erin King - who hoisted Lane aloft - had the presence of mind and sheer strength to save her team-mate from certain injury by somehow managing to prevent the scrum-half from toppling backwards, head first into the turf.\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 1080, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The almighty grimace on King's face showed just how much grit and determination it took to ensure her fellow countrywoman avoided a nasty fall from a great height.\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1106, \"end\": 1110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Art_of_Fighting\", \"score\": 0.9983332109237242, \"rank\": 0.0016452965122073903, \"text\": \"King\", \"types\": [\"Q7889\", \"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Art_of_Fighting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Art_of_Fighting\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Replays of the moments immediately began doing the rounds across social media and King has received universal praise, especially given the fact Ireland were well and truly out of the contest by that stage.\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1452, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1329, \"end\": 1333, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Art_of_Fighting\", \"score\": 0.9983332109237242, \"rank\": 0.0016452965122073903, \"text\": \"King\", \"types\": [\"Q7889\", \"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Art_of_Fighting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Art_of_Fighting\"}, {\"begin\": 1391, \"end\": 1398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9992482388969745, \"rank\": 0.000673678505819062, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I found a longer version of the clip:pic.twitter.com/YDeGrrrWEZ  Ultimately, indiscipline contributed to Ireland's downfall against Team GB, with Allan Temple-Jones' side losing two players - Stacey Flood\\u00a0andKing - to the sin bin during the heavy 28-12 loss.\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1712, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1559, \"end\": 1566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9992482388969745, \"rank\": 0.000673678505819062, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1586, \"end\": 1593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999859030915559, \"rank\": 1.4096224733314974e-05, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1676, \"end\": 1683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penalty_box\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"sin bin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penalty_box\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penalty_box\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meg Jones and Heather Cowell both crossed over for Team GB, while Claire Boles marked her Olympic debut with a late consolation try for Ireland after Megan Burns' earlier effort.\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1892, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1714, \"end\": 1717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meg_Griffin\", \"score\": 0.9999999559545368, \"rank\": 4.4040961309907936e-08, \"text\": \"Meg\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meg_Griffin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meg_Griffin\"}, {\"begin\": 1736, \"end\": 1742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simon_Cowell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0529713233781273e-19, \"text\": \"Cowell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simon_Cowell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simon_Cowell\"}, {\"begin\": 1765, \"end\": 1772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999859030915559, \"rank\": 1.4096224733314974e-05, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1780, \"end\": 1792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Claire_Boles\", \"score\": 0.9999909618412939, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Claire Boles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Claire_Boles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Claire_Boles\"}, {\"begin\": 1850, \"end\": 1857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9992482388969745, \"rank\": 0.000673678505819062, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1864, \"end\": 1875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Megan_Burns\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Megan Burns\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Megan_Burns\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Megan_Burns\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We have just got to learn.\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1921, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Playing in front of so many people at the Stade de France is unbelievable for us,' Ireland head coach Temple-Jones said.\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 2042, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1964, \"end\": 1979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}, {\"begin\": 2005, \"end\": 2012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9992482388969745, \"rank\": 0.000673678505819062, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"First time in the Olympics, first time for a lot of these young girls to get a go.\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2126, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'We are going to take lots of learnings from it moving forward.\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2191, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have got to grow the squad and grow the depth of our group.'\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2255, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He added: 'Exposing young girls to an Olympics like this and a stadium like this is going to be strength for both the 15s and Sevens squads, it's brilliant.\", \"from\": 2257, \"to\": 2413, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'To get girls playing on this stage and mixing between both squads on the 15s and Sevens side is unbelievable.\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2525, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'We hope the youngsters grow from this and move forward and be back in Los Angeles in four years' time.'\", \"from\": 2527, \"to\": 2631, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2598, \"end\": 2609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999132699172708, \"rank\": 8.673724302996526e-05, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2633, \"to\": 2681, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 2683, \"to\": 2753, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Simone Biles hits back at ex-United States teammate MyKayla Skinner over Olympic team criticism  ArrowMORE:Gymnast suffers nasty cut and black eye after scary fall but wins Olympic medal  ArrowMORE:When does Andy Murray play Olympic doubles quarter-final with Dan Evans?\", \"from\": 2755, \"to\": 3035, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2817, \"end\": 2832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MyKayla_Skinner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"MyKayla Skinner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MyKayla_Skinner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MyKayla_Skinner\"}, {\"begin\": 2973, \"end\": 2984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.267759380685224e-35, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 3025, \"end\": 3034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Die_Warzau\", \"score\": 0.9994320198049853, \"rank\": 0.0005683029796